ut a subscription you have access to Tables of Contents, Abstracts and more at no cost and without having to register.</dd>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"#online-manage\"><img border=\"0\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/down.gif\">Managing your Subscription to Journal of General Virology Online</a></strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"#print-manage\"><img border=\"0\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/down.gif\">Managing your Subscription to Journal of General Virology in Print</a></strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"/vir/institutional-faq.shtml\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">Any questions?</a></strong></dt>\n        <dt><strong><a href=\"/vir/print.shtml\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">How to subscribe to Journal of General Virology</a> including prices for 2008</strong></dt>\n      </dl>\n    </dd>\n  </dl>\n  <p><a name=\"online-manage\" id=\"online-manage\"></a></p>\n  <h2>Managing your Subscription to Journal of General Virology Online<a href=\"#top\"><img border=\"0\" hspace=\"3\" src=\"/icons/back.gif\"></a></h2>\n  <dl>\n    <dd>\n      <h2>Institutional Subscriptions</h2>\n      <dl>\n        <dd>\n          <img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\"><strong>Problems?</strong> Please read:<br>\n          <a href=\"/vir/institutional-faq.shtml\">Frequently Asked Questions about Institutional Subscriptions</a>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">Send us <a href=\"/vir/cgi/feedback\">Feedback</a> if you're unable to access the full text and your institution has a subscription to Journal of General Virology <strong><font color=\"#A70716\">ONLINE</font></strong>.\n          <p><strong>Account Administrator Only:</strong></p>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <a href=\"/cgi/changeuserinfo?ORIGJOURNAL=vir\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">How to view or change your Subscription Information</a>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <a href=\"/vir/rec_num.shtml\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">What to do if you forget your Subscriber Reference Number</a>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <a href=\"/cgi/changepwd?ORIGJOURNAL=vir\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">How to change the administrator User Name and/or Password</a>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <a href=\"/cgi/recnamepwd?ORIGJOURNAL=vir\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">What to do if you forget the administrator User Name and/or Password</a>\n        </dd>\n        <dd>\n          <a href=\"/vir/sub/instusage\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">View Your Institutional Usage Reports</a>\n        </dd>\n      </dl>\n      <p></p>\n      <dl>\n        <dt><strong>If you have questions related to your subscriptions, please contact the SGM Journal Sales office.</strong></dt>\n        <dd>\n          Office hours are 9 AM to 5 PM <font color=\"red\">UK time</font>.<br>\n          <strong>Society for General Microbiology</strong><br>\n          Marlborough House, Basingstoke Road<br>\n          Spencers Wood, Reading RG7 1AG<br>\n          +44 (0)118 988 1814<br>\n          +44 (0)118 988 5656<br>\n          <span id=\"em0\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n\n        </dd>\n      </dl>\n    </dd>\n  </dl>\n  <p><a name=\"print-manage\" id=\"print-manage\"></a></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <h3>Managing your Subscription to Journal of General Virology in Print<a href=\"#top\"><img border=\"0\" hspace=\"3\" src=\"/icons/back.gif\"></a></h3>\n  <dl>\n    <dt>Change of mailing address for the print journal</dt>\n    <dd>\n      Send email to <span id=\"em1\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n       and include the journal title, your subscriber number, OLD ADDRESS and new address. Please allow 4 weeks for the change of address to take effect.\n    </dd>\n    <dt>Report of missing issues for the print journal</dt>\n    <dd>\n      Send email to <span id=\"em2\">sgmjournals{at}sgm.ac.uk</span>\n       and include the journal title, your subscriber number and missed issue volume and part number. Please allow up to 10 weeks for receipt of the replacement issue, depending on where you are.\n    </dd>\n    <dt><strong><a href=\"/vir/print.shtml\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"11\" height=\"7\" hspace=\"6\" src=\"/icons/misc/arrowR.gif\">Prices and ordering information</a></strong></dt>\n  </dl>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#007E18\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color